data.description: Looking for the perfect blend of comfort and countryside serenity? This picturesque property has it all! Nestled on 3.1 acres, this 2-bedroom brick ranch offers a cozy interior with new paint and LVT flooring throughout. But that's not all – there's a fantastic pole barn too, providing ample space for your hobbies or storage needs. Embrace the countryside and the convenience of location in one incredible package. Just 15 Minutes to Sparta, Cookeville, Smithville - along with Burgess Falls and Center Hill Lake!
